Feature: Variant Editor


@productmanager
Scenario: Save variants on second page
    Given a product exists
        and the product has 7 properties
        and the user has opened the variant editor
    When the user switches to the next page
        and the user selects a variant in the variant table
        and the user saves the selected variant
    Then the selected variant is saved


@productmanager
Scenario: Keep filter after choosing view
    Given a product exists
        and the product has 2 properties
        and the product has 1 view
        and the view has 2 properties
        and the user has opened the variant editor
    When the user selects a filter for the table
        and the user selects a view
    Then the filter is still active
        and all variants are visible in the table
